<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="CSE Motors - Providing quality vehicles and services">
    <meta name="author" content="CSE Motors">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <title>CSE Motors</title>
    <!-- Link to external CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css" media="screen">
    
        
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content-container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="/images/site/icon.png" alt="CSE Motors Logo">
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <img src="/images/site/favicon-32x32.png" alt="CSE Motors Hero Image">
                <div class="hero-text">
                    <h1>Welcome to CSE Motors</h1>
                    <p>We provide quality vehicles and services</p>
                    <a href="#" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <img src="/images/site/checkerboard.jpg" alt="Feature 1 - Car Interior">
                    <h2>Feature 1</h2>
                    <p>Explore the luxurious interior of our cars, designed for comfort and style.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <img src="/images/site/own_today.png" alt="Feature 2 - Engine Performance">
                    <h2>Feature 2</h2>
                    <p>Experience the power and performance of our cutting-edge engines.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <img src="/images/site/small_check.png" alt="Feature 3 - Safety Features">
                    <h2>Feature 3</h2>
                    <p>Stay safe with our advanced safety features, ensuring peace of mind on the road.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="car-gallery">
                <div class="car-item">
                    <img src="/images/vehicles/adventador-tn.jpg" alt="Lamborghini Aventador">
                    <h3>Lamborghini Aventador</h3>
                    <p>A high-performance sports car with a V12 engine, offering thrilling speed and style.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="car-item">
                    <img src="/images/vehicles/fire-truck.jpg" alt="Fire Truck">
                    <h3>Fire Truck</h3>
                    <p>A powerful emergency vehicle, equipped with all the essential tools for firefighting.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="car-item">
                    <img src="/images/vehicles/survan.jpg" alt="SUV">
                    <h3>Family SUV</h3>
                    <p>A spacious and reliable family SUV with ample seating and modern features for comfort.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2025 CSE Motors. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
